#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:735
msgid "``WHERE``"
msgstr "``WHERE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:395
msgid ""
"Defines with a SQL \"WHERE\" statement which features should be selected "
