msgstr ""
"Definiše SQL „WHERE“ iskazom koji objekti treba da budu izabrani iz ulaznog "
"sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:397
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:741
msgid "**Group N features per transaction (Default: 2000)**"
msgstr "**Grupiši N objekata po transakciji (Podrazumevano: 2000)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:400
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:744
msgid "``GT``"
msgstr "``GT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:404
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:748
msgid ""
"You can group the input features in transactions where N defines the size. "
"By default N limits the transaction size to 20000 features."
msgstr ""
"Možete grupisati ulazne objekte u transakcije gde N definiše veličinu. "
"Podrazumevano N ograničava veličinu transakcije na 20000 objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:407
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:751
msgid "**Overwrite existing table**"
msgstr "**Prepiši postojeću tabelu**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:408
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:752
msgid "``OVERWRITE``"
msgstr "``OVERWRITE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:411
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:467
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:473
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:755
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:811
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:817
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:892
msgid "Default: True"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: True"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:412
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:756
msgid ""
"If there is a table with the same name in the database, and if this option "
"is set to True, the table will be overwritten."
msgstr ""
"Ako u bazi podataka postoji tabela istog naziva i ako je ova opcija "
"postavljena na True, tabela će biti prepisana."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:415
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:759
msgid "**Append to existing table**"
msgstr "**Dodaj na postojeću tabelu**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:416
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:760
msgid "``APPEND``"
msgstr "``APPEND``"

