#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:764
msgid ""
"If checked / True the vector data will be appended to an existing table. New"
" fields found in the input layer are ignored. By default a new table will be"
" created."
msgstr ""
"Ako je uključeno / True, vektorski podaci biće dodati na postojeću tabelu. "
"Nova polja pronađena u ulaznom sloju se zanemaruju. Podrazumevano se pravi "
"nova tabela."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:424
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:768
msgid "**Append and add new fields to existing table**"
msgstr "**Dodaj i dodaj nova polja na postojeću tabelu**"

