msgid ""
"If activated the vector data will be appended to an existing table, there "
"won't be a new table created. New fields found in input layer are added to "
"the table. By default a new table will be created."
msgstr ""
"Ako je aktivirano, vektorski podaci biće dodati na postojeću tabelu, neće se"
" praviti nova tabela. Nova polja pronađena u ulaznom sloju dodaju se u "
"tabelu. Podrazumevano se pravi nova tabela."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:434
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:778
msgid "**Do not launder columns/table names**"
msgstr "**Ne pročišćavaj nazive kolona/tabela**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:435
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:779
msgid "``LAUNDER``"
msgstr "``LAUNDER``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:439
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:783
msgid ""
"With this option checked you can prevent the default behaviour (converting "
"column names to lowercase, removing spaces and other invalid characters)."
msgstr ""
"Sa uključenom ovom opcijom možete sprečiti podrazumevano ponašanje "
"(pretvaranje naziva kolona u mala slova, uklanjanje razmaka i drugih "
"neispravnih znakova)."

