#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:805
msgid ""
"Applies cleanup operations on geometries to ensure they are valid regarding "
"the rules of the `Simple Features specification "
"<https://www.ogc.org/standards/sfs/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Primenjuje operacije čišćenja na geometrijama kako bi bile ispravne prema "
"pravilima `specifikacije Simple Features "
"<https://www.ogc.org/standards/sfs/>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:463
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:807
msgid "**Promote to Multipart**"
msgstr "**Unapredi u višedelnu**"

