msgstr "Pretvara tip geometrije objekata u višedelni u izlaznoj tabeli"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:469
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/vectormiscellaneous.rst:813
